Ocean acidification, or 300 million years, the fastest ultra<br/><br/>One study showed that the ocean may be 300 million years, the fastest acidification, more than four times during the mass extermination of life on Earth history. The researchers concluded that the previous ocean acidification, the main factor is the &quot;act of God&quot;, there is now a &quot;man-made.
